---
---
<section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">For Adults 40+</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Created especially for people navigating midlife cardiovascular challenges</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Problem 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">High Blood Pressure</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Your readings are creeping up. The doctor mentioned "lifestyle changes" but didn't explain what that means. We give you the exact protocol to bring those numbers down naturally.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Problem 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-yellow-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">High Cholesterol</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Your LDL is elevated and statins are on the table. But what if you could improve your lipid panel through targeted nutrition? We've helped thousands do exactly that.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Problem 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Prediabetes</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">With so much conflicting advice about blood sugar, knowing what to eat can feel impossible. We simplify it with clear, actionable guidance.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Problem 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Family History</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Heart disease runs in your family. You're determined to break the pattern. Our prevention-focused approach helps you stack the deck in your favor.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Problem 5 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.354 15.354A9 9 0 018.646 3.646 9.003 9.003 0 0012 21a9.003 9.003 0 008.354-5.646z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Low Energy</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">You're tired all the time. Coffee isn't cutting it anymore. Often, cardiovascular health and energy are directly connected. Let's fix both.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Problem 6 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Medication Side Effects</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">The pills help your numbers but make you feel terrible. What if there was another way? Many of our members work with their doctors to reduce or eliminate medications.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
